Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}你的意思我明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}…我这也是逼不得已！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}人类就是毫无来由地爱将注意力集中在重点以外的动物！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}…比起赛况却更在意写在胸前的赞助商名称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}居然叫BINBO…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}…比起电影剧情却更在意木村○哉胡子的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}高…胡子的位置实在是高…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}…比起案件本身却更在意嫌疑犯的怪异姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}居然叫宇宙太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}一旦开始在意这些小事  它们便会存在于脑海之中挥之不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnKaiTi\fs32\2c&H000000&\3c&HA00000&\4c&H000000&\b1}…最终导致完全不记得丝毫的重点内容
